      "note": "The messenger of Allah must strive his utmost to proclaim the Message of Allah: as for results, it is not for him to command them. He must wait patiently, in the knowledge that he is not forgotten by Allah, but is constantly under Allah's eyes?under His loving care and protection. And he must glorify Allah's name, as he is a standard-bearer of Allah's Truth."
